The new virus is coming out, animals are changed into deadly zombies therefore, do not be lazy and do not sit still, but take the AKM and other modern weapons and clear the missions. Moreover, the post-apocalyptic world contains rich resources, and many interesting things in forgotten laboratories, military bases, bunkers and other strategic points. You are only last hope to find the shelter of another last survivor and destroy them in free survival zombie crafting game.



After the Zombies Attack, all military bases that are caught in the middle of a zombie warfare, lost and left to dead, you must put your military training and weapon handling skills to get back the cities as a sniper shooter in free zombie survival game. As a weapon expert, you must use the trigger any weapon at your disposal to shoot your way through hordes of zombies, Animal Zombies and become a real survival Hunter.

Clear the areas streets, cities, Army basis and public places from these deadly zombies. This a cool Zombie survival strategy action assassinated game.
